Ingredients
1 lb Korean eggplant
2 to 3 cloves garlic, chopped
1 to 2 green onions, chopped
2 tbsp soy sauce
1 tbsp agave nectar, honey or sugar
1 tbsp sesame oil
1 to 2 tsp gochugaru, Korean red pepper flakes
2 tsp sesame seeds
pinch of black pepper
